  "closing": {
    "headline": "The project no longer looks like a concept sketch.",
    "body": "The most interesting change is not a single feature. It is that architecture, execution, public entry, and product canon are starting to reinforce each other. That is the point where a serious internal system turns into something people can eventually use, trust, and follow."
